            "stanza_text": "Jeunesse, adieu ! car j'ai beau faire,\nJ'ai beau t'étreindre et te presser,\nJ'ai beau gémir et t'embrasser,\nNous fuyons en pays contraire."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Ton souffle tiède est si charmant !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "On est si beau sous ta couronne !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Tiens : ce baiser que je te donne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Laisse-le durer un moment.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ton souffle tiède est si charmant !\nOn est si beau sous ta couronne !\nTiens : ce baiser que je te donne,\nLaisse-le durer un moment."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Ce long baiser, douce chérie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Si c'est notre adieu sans retour,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Ne le romps pas jusqu'au détour",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "De cette haie encor fleurie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ce long baiser, douce chérie,\nSi c'est notre adieu sans retour,\nNe le romps pas jusqu'au détour\nDe cette haie encor fleurie !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Si j'ai mal porté tes couleurs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Ce n'est pas ma faute, ô jeunesse !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Le vent glacé de la tristesse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Hâte bien la chute des fleurs !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si j'ai mal porté tes couleurs,\nCe n'est pas ma faute, ô jeunesse !\nLe vent glacé de la tristesse\nHâte bien la chute des fleurs !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Mais, ô Dieu ! par combien de portes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Reviennent tes jours triomphans !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Et que de fleurs tu me rapportes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Sur la tête de mes enfans !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais, ô Dieu ! par combien de portes\nReviennent tes jours triomphans !\nEt que de fleurs tu me rapportes\nSur la tête de mes enfans !"
